19
00:03:10,988 --> 00:03:19,404
Nor did wild rumors of all sorts fail to exaggerate, and still the more horrify the true histories of these deadly encounters.

20
00:03:20,145 --> 00:03:32,608
For not only do fabulous rumors naturally grow out of the very body of all surprising, terrible events, as the smitten tree gives birth to its fungi, but, in maritime life,

21
