Far more than in that of terra firma, wild rumors abound, wherever there is any adequate reality for them to cling to.

22
00:03:40,863 --> 00:03:48,977
And as the sea surpasses the land in this matter, so the whale fishery surpasses every other sort of maritime life.

23
00:03:48,957 --> 00:03:54,593
