25
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:11,279
They are by all odds the most directly brought into contact with whatever is appallingly astonishing in the sea.

26
00:04:12,161 --> 00:04:19,842
Face to face they not only eye its greatest marvels, but, hand to jaw, give battle to them, alone,

27
00:04:19,822 --> 00:04:33,785
In such remotest waters, that though you sailed a thousand miles, and passed a thousand shores, you would not come to any chiseled hearthstone, or ought hospitable beneath that part of the sun.

28
00:04:33,845 --> 00:04:45,103
