114
00:21:48,029 --> 00:22:09,700
Gnawed within and scorched without, with the infixed, unrelenting fangs of some incurable idea such in one, could he be found, would seem the very man to dart his iron and lift his lance against the most appalling of all brutes, or, if for any reason thought to be corporarily incapacitated for that,

115
00:22:09,882 --> 00:22:16,795
