116
00:22:16,815 --> 00:22:28,937
But be all this as it may, certain it is, that with the mad secret of his unabated rage bolted up and keyed in him, Ahab had purposely sailed upon the present voyage

117
00:22:28,917 --> 00:22:33,883
with the one only and all-engrossing object of hunting, the white whale.

118
00:22:33,983 --> 00:22:47,400
