119
00:22:47,600 --> 00:22:53,608
They were bent on profitable cruises, the profit to be counted down in dollars from lament.

120
00:22:53,588 --> 00:22:58,874
He was intent on an audacious, immitigable, and supernatural revenge.

121
00:22:59,054 --> 00:23:06,822
Here, then, was this grey-headed, ungodly old man, chasing, with curses, a job's whale round the world.

122
00:23:07,543 --> 00:23:20,777
